<section id="itsm_locQualityIssuesRef">
    <title>its_locQualityIssuesRef</title>
    
    <para>Localization Quality Standoff Reference - the <code>its_locQualityIssuesRef</code>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>
        is the <olink targetdoc="../xliff21.xml" targetptr="ITS20">[ITS]</olink> defined
            <code>its_locQualityIssuesRef</code>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>.</para>
    <para>This
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>
        references the collection of Localization Issues that pertain to the content span from where
        the reference is declared.</para>
    <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><emphasis>Type:</emphasis>
        string.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> IRI</para>
        
    <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined.</para>
    
    
    <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
            targetdoc="../../elements/inline/mrk.xml" targetptr="mrk"><code>&lt;mrk></code></olink>
        and <?oxy_custom_end?><olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/sm.xml" targetptr="sm"
                ><code>sm</code></olink>.</para>
    
    
    <para>See the <olink targetdoc="../../modules/itsm/Localization_Quality_Issue.xml"
            targetptr="lqiAnnotation">ITS Localization Issue Annotation</olink> for the normative
        usage description of this
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>. </para>
    <itemizedlist>
        <title>Constraints</title>
        <listitem>
            <para>The IRI value of the <link linkend="itsm_locQualityIssuesRef"
                    >its_locQualityIssuesRef</link>
                <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>
                <glossterm>must</glossterm> be an IRI referencing a <olink
                    targetdoc="../../elements/itsm/itsm_locQualityIssues.xml"
                    targetptr="itsm_locQualityIssues"><code>its_locQualityIssues</code></olink>
                array element within the same <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/unit.xml"
                    targetptr="unit"><code>unit</code></olink>.</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para>Multiple <link linkend="itsm_locQualityIssuesRef">locQualityIssuesRef</link>
                <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>propert<?oxy_custom_end?>ies
                    <glossterm>may</glossterm> reference the same <olink
                    targetdoc="../../elements/itsm/itsm_locQualityIssues.xml"
                    targetptr="itsm_locQualityIssues"><code>its_locQualityIssues</code></olink>
                array element.</para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
    <itemizedlist>
        <title>Processing Requirements</title>
        <listitem>
            <para><firstterm>Modifiers</firstterm> removing the last <link
                    linkend="itsm_locQualityIssuesRef"><code>its_locQualityIssuesRef</code></link>
                <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>
                referencing a <olink targetptr="itsm_locQualityIssues"
                    targetdoc="../../elements/itsm/itsm_locQualityIssues.xml"
                        ><code>its_locQualityIssues</code></olink> array element
                    <glossterm>must</glossterm> delete that <olink
                    targetptr="itsm_provenanceRecords"
                    targetdoc="../../elements/itsm/itsm_provenanceRecords.xml"
                        ><code>its_locQualityIssues</code></olink> array element.</para>
        </listitem>
        
    </itemizedlist>
</section>
